TextBody:
Hello Eugene,
 
Thank you for your time today.
In today's meeting, we reviewed the setting for the NEA Development environment.
You will upgrade the Dev. environment to test the new Netwrix Access Analyzer before you can upgrade the Production environment.
 
Before the upgrade meeting, you will take a snapshot of the NEA Application and SQL servers.
Download all necessary installation files from https://www.netwrix.com/my_products.html
  
Please right-click on the zip file and click Properties to unblock the file before copying it to the application server before our meeting.
 
You can use the link below to schedule the upgrade meeting for your DEV environment.
https://nwxcorp.my.salesforce-sites.com/cts?Id=uFnIihHkupUjPewvtF_HU.xpew7CmFQ5yd_b9qEt1cM-Z&MeetingID=s_4lMiqrMfKbpnyM7_D70pitBa1.XQqXRSaT468MpC4-Z

TextBody:
Hello Eugene,

Thank you for taking the time to meet today.

Today we:
Upgraded your Netwrix Access Analyzer and Access Information center to version 12.0
We verified that the Access Analyzer was working and that the single sign on and ssl were working in the AIC.
We replaced the AIC certificate binding with the new certificate and we added single sign on to your reporting console.

I am glad that we were able to get your issue resolved. The following is a summary of the ticket for your records.

Symptom
Proactive upgrade of dev environment to 12.0


Resolution
Upgraded your Netwrix Access Analyzer and Access Information center to version 12.0
We verified that the Access Analyzer was working and that the single sign on and ssl were working in the AIC.
We replaced the AIC certificate binding with the new certificate and we added single sign on to your reporting console.

Following this email, you will receive an automated confirmation that the case is closed, along with the ability to re-open the case if any related errors return. In addition, you will also receive a separate email with a survey where you can let us know how we did. Feel free to leave any feedback via the survey link!
Thank you,
Ian Ranstrom
Senior Technical Support Engineer
__________________ _________
Powerful Data Security Made Easy
6160 Warren Parkway, Suite 100, Frisco, TX 75034
www.netwrix.com
